Third-Party Components

This software integrates with the following third-party libraries, which are not
distributed with this package but may be required for specific functionality:

- CREDICI – https://github.com/IDSIA/credici
- CREMA – https://github.com/IDSIA/crema

These libraries are:

- Copyright (c) IDSIA
- Licensed under the GNU Lesser General Public License v3.0 (LGPL-3.0)

These components are accessed dynamically via Java (JVM) through `jpype`, and retain
their original licenses. Users of this software must comply with the licensing terms
of these components when using functionality that depends on them.
